    have h4 : ‚ÄĖcfc_toLinearFunctional ha x y‚ÄĖ ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖx‚ÄĖ * ‚ÄĖy‚ÄĖ := cfc_toLinearFunctional_bound x y
    nlinarith [h3, h4, norm_nonneg (f : C((spectrum ‚Ąā a), ‚Ąā)), norm_nonneg (x : H), norm_nonneg (y : H)]
  linarith [h2]

/-- The total variation of the complex measure `E_{a, x,y}` bounded by `‚ÄĖx‚ÄĖ * ‚ÄĖy‚ÄĖ`.
Rudin "Real and complex analysis" Theorem 6.19 (2), combined with the bound by
